Class LongStaticHistogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.histogram.AbstractStaticHistogram
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.histogram.LongStaticHistogram
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Histogram, LongHistogram
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LongDynamicHistogram

    public class LongStaticHistogram
extends AbstractStaticHistogram
implements LongHistogram
    Histogram class storing long values. The histogram will start with "bin" bins, but it can grow dynamically to the left and right.
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
